==English==
===Etymology===
{{wikipedia}}
Named after [[w:Jan Oort|Jan Oort]].

===Noun===
'''Oort cloud'''
#{{astronomy}} A [[roughly]] [[spherical]] [[region]] of [[space]] from 50,000 to 100,000 [[astronomical unit]]s (approximately 1 [[light year]]) from the [[sun]]; [[supposedly]] the [[source]] of most [[comet]]s.

